      "content": "# Focus: quality\n\nToday's date: May 26 2026\n\n## Task\nAnalyze this codebase for coding conventions and testing patterns.\n\n## Write these documents to .planning/codebase/:\n- CONVENTIONS.md - Code style, naming, patterns, error handling\n- TESTING.md - Framework, structure, mocking, coverage\n\n## IMPORTANT:\n- Use May 26 2026 for all [YYYY-MM-DD] date placeholders in documents.\n- Scope: (full repo) — explore the entire codebase.\n- Explore thoroughly using Glob, Grep, and Bash tools.\n- Write documents directly using templates.\n- Return confirmation only with file paths and line counts.\n\n## Agent Skills to Load:\n- stack-l3-vitest (if vitest detected)\n- stack-l3-zod (if zod patterns found)\n\n## Document Templates (follow these structures):\n\n### CONVENTIONS.md Structure:\n```markdown\n# Code Conventions\n\n[Generated: 2026-05-26]\n\n## Overview\nSummary of coding conventions used in this project.\n\n## Code Style\n- Linter: [e.g., ESLint, Biome]\n- Formatter: [e.g., Prettier, Biome]\n- Style guide: [e.g., Airbnb, Standard]\n\n## Naming Conventions\n- Files and directories\n- Variables and constants\n- Functions and methods\n- Classes and components\n- Type definitions\n\n## Patterns\n- Common design patterns used\n- Module organization\n- File structure patterns\n\n## Error Handling\n- Error types and structures\n- Try-catch patterns\n- Error propagation\n\n## Code Organization\n- Import organization\n- File structure\n- Component organization\n```\n\n### TESTING.md Structure:\n```markdown\n# Testing Strategy\n\n[Generated: 2026-05-26]\n\n## Overview\nTesting approach and coverage strategy.\n\n## Testing Framework\n- Framework name and version\n- Configuration files\n- Setup and teardown\n\n## Test Structure\n- Unit test organization\n- Integration test organization\n- E2E test organization\n\n## Mocking Strategy\n- Mocking library\n- Mock patterns used\n- Stub implementations\n\n## Coverage\n- Coverage tools\n- Target coverage\n- Current coverage\n\n## Test Commands\n- Running all tests\n- Running specific test files\n- Coverage reporting\n```\n\n## Success Criteria:\n- [ ] CONVENTIONS.md created with >40 lines\n- [ ] TESTING.md created with >40 lines\n- [ ] Documents include actual file paths with backticks\n- [ ] Clear testing framework identified\n\nReturn format:\n```\n## Mapping Complete\n\n**Focus:** quality\n**Documents written:**\n- `.planning/codebase/CONVENTIONS.md` ({N} lines)\n- `.planning/codebase/TESTING.md` ({N} lines)\n\nReady for orchestrator summary.\n```",
